{"tid":1753080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母林鄭，民意呀！睇撚到未呀？！","createTime":"2019-11-25T01:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T03:31:21.000Z","uid":51111,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"58e0428fab316f4269e305da66d6f003455b0aa1","tid":1753080,"uid":51111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:17:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">6月9之後第一次咁撚開心呀！屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係！</span>五大訴求未撚回應架！要繼續行動！<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以平日搞多啲和理非行動先，好似以前咁唱歌，默哀，叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n星期六，日遊行加開花。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f7e75a3b04ab22d03196b5cccedadf0b345dbb","tid":1753080,"uid":161374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:18:11.000Z","msg":"民意從來唔係佢考慮範圍"},{"pid":"189825d6272cf387f054e3bac1153465d0644564","tid":1753080,"uid":27432,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:18:55.000Z","msg":"林奠：區議會未能真實反應民意，我睇到既係大部份市民都好支持政府，支持警察。"},{"pid":"41ae98f3ce384005433a9a5cd2d6bddaacd95ed2","tid":1753080,"uid":29080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:20:18.000Z","msg":"佢會話沉默大多數未投<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df08ddf1b019d408bc29ad6f83b225f5468aff7","tid":1753080,"uid":51111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:21:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16a6bb3495c6302e3d650cba037d17851b99210d","tid":1753080,"uid":51111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:22:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2143ca001